{"tid":2273830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點先證明到選舉舞弊","createTime":"2020-11-06T04:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T10:01:17.000Z","uid":73407,"like":24,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"879fc569cfd694c068fa21af09b444e8638ee23f","tid":2273830,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:26:37.000Z","msg":"首先選票一拆封就係不記名<br />\n如果佢加左新選票<br />\n掉左Trump選票<br />\n只要個總數係match到總投票人數就唔會check到<br />\n同埋所有現場投票停哂<br />\n新票係poll book 度求其劃落個未投既人名度就得<br />\n就算你要求重點 D票都入哂去 點幾多次都係咁<br />\n<br />\n關於死人投票  或者偷親人票黎投 <br />\n全部都要逐單求證 比你證明到都係個別例子<br />\n只要你搵唔到幾萬張死人投票都唔影響<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnWYak6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqnWYak6.png&h=43f742f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGeorgia有監票員發現53張不明來歷選票放上枱面<br />\n搵多兩個工作人員話無問題<br />\n個法官要求佢證明堆選票係幾時入票站<br />\n大佬佢一個人唔會睇哂成個站<br />\n根本唔會追蹤到每一張無記認既票幾時入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-election-2020/trump-election-georgia-lawsuit-voter-fraud-b1621163.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Famericas%2Fus-election-2020%2Ftrump-election-georgia-lawsuit-voter-fraud-b1621163.html&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=e0aa671c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/us-election-2020/trump-election-georgia-lawsuit-voter-fraud-b1621163.html</a><br />\n<br />\n賓州直頭唔比GOP監票員入<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2273367/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2273367/page/1</a><br />\nGeorgia 票站叫GOP監票員番屋企訓<br />\n自己閉門慢慢點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2273367/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2273367/page/1</a><br />\nDetroit 點票區封木板<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1324139647111409667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1324139647111409667&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=faf4fa9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1324139647111409667&h=32db0824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1324139647111409667</a><br />\n<br />\n同時有138K選票投同一個人?<br />\n入錯數字 正常<br />\n點極都有選票? 唔記得禁upload?<br />\n工作人員睇漏 正常<br />\n新選票9成投拜登?<br />\nTrumpr叫唔好郵寄選票 正常<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMHTJKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMHTJKL.jpg&h=91369168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MA8a2g6tTp0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMA8a2g6tTp0&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=9bedcefe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MA8a2g6tTp0</a>"},{"pid":"dae9673e7600e1a266a88e9a64f8b26ecc1f49f9","tid":2273830,"uid":73407,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:30:43.000Z","msg":"問題唔係有無舞弊<br />\n係就算有舞弊都證明唔到<br />\n連監票員親眼見到都不受理"},{"pid":"93531eb4a833bd38c4502ae8a56fdcbd61fbc939","tid":2273830,"uid":242537,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/123547032_1283239202034035_2748349684791423566_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=825194&amp;_nc_ohc=CNZh99HBLyQAX9AXct2&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=44e3b9d5e68352f6bf6c4fe9b285606c&amp;oe=5FCB3A63\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F123547032_1283239202034035_2748349684791423566_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D825194%26_nc_ohc%3DCNZh99HBLyQAX9AXct2%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D44e3b9d5e68352f6bf6c4fe9b285606c%26oe%3D5FCB3A63&h=0a5b1d2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"094fe326a4f4ff042c89715f7d6f8dd4810c92a0","tid":2273830,"uid":73407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:37:59.000Z","msg":"賓州高等法院10月23日宣佈<br />\n簽名唔岩都照計<br />\n<br />\n美賓州法院放行郵寄選票 簽名不一致也要計入<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/10/23/n12497599.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F20%2F10%2F23%2Fn12497599.htm&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=adf68b5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/20/10/23/n12497599.htm</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.politico.com/news/2020/10/23/pennsylvania-court-ballot-signatures-431794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F10%2F23%2Fpennsylvania-court-ballot-signatures-431794&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=64c7c9dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.politico.com/news/2020/10/23/pennsylvania-court-ballot-signatures-431794</a><br />\n<br />\n「禁止選舉委員會基於縣選舉官員或雇員進行簽名比較，並依此拒絕缺席或郵寄選票，同時，也不接受任何第三方以簽名分析和比較為由提起訴訟。」"},{"pid":"08d7cca61797104eef9ee21f766369dcb04bf35b","tid":2273830,"uid":250773,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"好似話有barcode<br />\n追蹤唔到邊個 但追蹤到張票係咪valid <br />\n一係有能力做到valid票<br />\n一係整假選民<br />\n但冇實例點討論<br />\n<br />\n所以首先你要了解美國選舉張票由生產到開票個流動 所有選舉安排 登記填法 一班生活係香港嘅人點會知個漏洞係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a44aad2f8f9c33b66cfd7cbdc64842a383dbbf","tid":2273830,"uid":233470,"like":6,"dislike":31,"score":-25,"quote":{"pid":"93531eb4a833bd38c4502ae8a56fdcbd61fbc939","tid":2273830,"uid":242537,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/123547032_1283239202034035_2748349684791423566_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=825194&amp;_nc_ohc=CNZh99HBLyQAX9AXct2&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=44e3b9d5e68352f6bf6c4fe9b285606c&amp;oe=5FCB3A63\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg