hkg.com/thread/2273367/page/1</a><br />\nDetroit 點票區封木板<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1324139647111409667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1324139647111409667&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=faf4fa9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1324139647111409667&h=32db0824\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1324139647111409667</a><br />\n<br />\n同時有138K選票投同一個人?<br />\n入錯數字 正常<br />\n點極都有選票? 唔記得禁upload?<br />\n工作人員睇漏 正常<br />\n新選票9成投拜登?<br />\nTrumpr叫唔好郵寄選票 正常<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LMHTJKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLMHTJKL.jpg&h=91369168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MA8a2g6tTp0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMA8a2g6tTp0&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=9bedcefe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MA8a2g6tTp0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:46:15.000Z","msg":"&quot;&quot;只要個總數係match到總投票人數就唔會check到&quot; any solution?"},{"pid":"f8bc3c83266000fee73b3be8a72342cf6045e2dd","tid":2273830,"uid":110109,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T05:46:47.000Z","msg":"樓主立論確實無問題<br />\n要證明舞弊可能真係難過舞弊<br />\n但係現實政治環境就係咁，真係無乜乎<br />\n<br />\n個套法律係美國人自己同意嘅<br />\n指控人要舉證<br />\n除非美國人自己唔同意<br />\n所以先要有法院，法院都唔信，就得返拳頭<br />\n<br />\n至於局外人，都係講你信唔信美國套制度<br />\n唔信嘅 討論結束"},{"pid":"c485bb625649f91558152939ecf168186c44c6ff","tid":2273830,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e24addce094d2d01d4cc2019306405a939e5067a","tid":2273830,"uid":73407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08d7cca61797104eef9ee21f766369dcb04bf35b","tid":2273830,"uid":250773,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04: